title: If You Understand This Simple Concept, You Can Achieve Anything
description: “We are all inventors, each sailing out on a voyage of discovery, guided each by a private chart, of which there is no duplicate. The world is all gates, all opportunities.” ― Ralph Waldo Emerson “People are capable, at any time in their lives, of doing what they dream of.” ― Paulo Coelho.   Music Sources Fearless Motivation - Take Responsibility Website: http://www.fearlessmotivation.com/ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/fearlessmotivationofficial Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCf9_s9ii6BZ-klpgmtIi3WQ Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/artist/1FhamVtJlNqaekPnwxQpbk
